{"tid":1926362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁凱晴banner 被廢老抹屎上去","createTime":"2020-03-15T05:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:03:07.000Z","uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"be0d62a8070d06c5fbfd2fc1d9ed207dd9d3e73a","tid":1926362,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"【不只是文明的差距】<br />\n<br />\n以往我哋嘅橫額已試過兩次被親共派支持者塗上大便，但未試過好似今次咁多，多到令我懷疑比一個成年人單次嘅排便量更多。<br />\n<br />\n老實講咁大面積嘅糞便我哋團隊已經冇辦法再自行處理，因此已經通知政府部門要求盡快協助清洗。<br />\n<br />\n面對呢種破壞者，「人一藍腦便殘」都遠遠不足以形容，你哋係一班停留於肛門期嘅親共巨嬰。<br />\n<br />\n#親共就係呢個水平<br />\n#肛門期巨嬰<br />\n#好玩唔玩玩屎<br />\n#我屋企隻貓都識得去沙盤解決<br />\n#隔住個mon都聞到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖就唔貼 要睇上晴b fb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/324089788475814/posts/498436054374519/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F324089788475814%2Fposts%2F498436054374519%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=8481132c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/324089788475814/posts/498436054374519/</a>"},{"pid":"550fb900014e5dc627ba63d27c44d420cf3f8289","tid":1926362,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b974554dd11df9164ad454838dc13787a6f90f1","tid":1926362,"uid":218082,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv9XPtH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv9XPtH.jpg&h=1f4dfbba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f428c1f2d68ae2d8d9df85a2a1b4d0c0f464180","tid":1926362,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1f4941712217607ccee71112449ea23c4b3dac","tid":1926362,"uid":147784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:40:32.000Z","msg"